window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Meet Mickey Friday: San Diego’s newest werewolf private investigator.</b></p><p>In a city where shifters—werewolves, bears, cougars, and more—live in secret, Mickey Friday is trying to carve out her niche. Street-smart but still building her reputation, most of her cases involve tracking down cheating spouses and solving petty mysteries. That changes when Mrs. Laine, a wealthy werewolf, hires her to recover stolen heirlooms. The catch? The suspects are bear shifters, and Mrs. Laine doesn’t want the police involved.</p><p>As Mickey digs into the case, her love life takes a surprising twist with the arrival of a charming cougar shifter. But when her investigation leads her straight into the dangerous world of shifter politics—and a young werewolf turns up dead on her doorstep—Mickey realizes she’s stepped into something far more dangerous than she bargained for.</p><p>With tensions rising and predators closing in, Mickey must navigate a maze of secrets, alliances, and betrayals, where every move could be her last.</p><p><b><i>Wolf City</i> is the start of a thrilling new series packed with mystery, danger, and a touch of romance.</b><br><br><i><b>Click BUY NOW or READ FOR FREE today!</b></i></p>"; 
